<h1 align="center">
<span><i>Adapters</i></span>
</h1>

<h3 align="center">
A Unified Library for Parameter-Efficient and Modular Transfer Learning
</h3>
<h3 align="center">
    <a href="https://adapterhub.ml">ğŸŒ Website</a>
